And at $800, the fake fireplace
is a real bargain.

45:11.952 --> 45:14.086
Don't play with that, fellas.

45:14.088 --> 45:15.221
Sorry.

45:18.092 --> 45:20.726
Oh, Linda, what can I say.

45:20.728 --> 45:23.530
You are like the Peggy Guggenheim
of high school theater.

45:23.532 --> 45:24.730
But prettier.

45:33.842 --> 45:36.443
I don't believe this.

45:36.445 --> 45:39.880
- Linda, just relax...
