45:54.963 --> 45:56.963
You've left me no choice.

45:56.965 --> 45:58.966
Linda.

45:58.968 --> 46:00.668
- Linda!
- Oh my God. My parents are going to kill me!

46:00.670 --> 46:01.903
No, no, no. It's fine.

46:01.905 --> 46:03.671
