58:53.277 --> 58:54.710
No, no. I need to talk to you.

58:54.712 --> 58:56.578
Take the chair inside, please.

59:00.485 --> 59:02.518
How's your neck?

59:02.520 --> 59:04.654
Just say what you need to say
and leave me alone.

59:05.990 --> 59:08.591
Is it true? Did you lie
to Jason about the play?

59:09.894 --> 59:11.562
Yes. Yes, I did.

59:12.797 --> 59:14.897
I don't believe it.

59:14.899 --> 59:17.400
What kind of teacher are you?

59:17.402 --> 59:20.603
